reviews.review_text: Upgrade / 2017 updated audience source An absolutely stellar audience recording.  One-of-a-kind show.  Spring 86' has some great shows on the east coast.  This be one of em'.
Best of the bunch Several good aud sources for this one.  I feel this is the best sounding one.
